alue isn=E2=80=99t monetary. When I received an invitation for the press pr=
eview for the Brooklyn Museum=E2=80=99s exhibition of sculptor <b>Elizabeth=
 Catlett</b>=E2=80=99s work, I was reminded that it was time to look over t=
he museum calendar and start planning my autumn trips with Mrs. Wall Power.=
